{
  "stem": "2118.4",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "There was no water in the camp, no water, period.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "A guy came.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "And they had a water hose.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 68,
      "text": "First, they shaved us, cut off the hair with their machines.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 69,
      "text": "Then they had this big tank.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 70,
      "text": "And we walked over.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 71,
      "text": "And it was a case.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 72,
      "text": "We were standing in a line.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 73,
      "text": "And they told you to get into that tank.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 74,
      "text": "It was like a-- like a big bowl, like a small jacuzzi or something like that.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 75,
      "text": "And they grabbed you on the side, and they dipped you in it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 76,
      "text": "And this was Lysol, a mix of Lysol.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 77,
      "text": "And when I got out, this was burning like fire.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 78,
      "text": "They told you close your eyes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 79,
      "text": "Because they just cut my hair and cut my hair.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 80,
      "text": "And I imagine the machines they use weren't the best.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 81,
      "text": "You were nicked.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 82,
      "text": "And it burned like fire and there was no water.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 83,
      "text": "And then they-- somebody came with a big hose.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 84,
      "text": "And they sprayed us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "580 people-- can you imagine being sprayed with a hose, with one hose?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And you tried to get there, to catch a little of that hose, which I don't think I even made it.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then they-- we went back and took that clothing which we-- which we brought in the first place.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, this was a lucky streak.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because before they sent us out from-- from Cieszanow, they took us to select clothing at an army base and-- and-- and divide it and things.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I went in that place.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there was clothing piled to the ceiling from prisoners, from Russian prisoners, all kinds of prisoners-- maybe American, English.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I picked out the best [NON-ENGLISH], [NON-ENGLISH], what they call undershirts, everything.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I picked out a pair of shoes, you understand, instead of having those wooden clogs.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
